---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Put AI to Work — nad Let Your Business Run Itself"
  subtitle="AI works better, faster and cheaper than any employee — and it never takes a break."
  ctaText="Test It Now for Free"
  ctaHref=""
  valueExpression="AI isn't optional, it's inevitable. Early adopters win big — be late and get left behind."
  heroImage={{
    src: heroImage.src,
    rotated: true
  }}
>
  <section class="pt-20" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
    <h2 id="problem-heading" class="text-4xl text-zinc-100 text-center font-semibold">The Problem</h2>
    <p class="text-secondary text-center mt-5">Running a business means juggling many tasks. Without automation, you're losing energy, time, money and customers every single day.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-4 mt-20 gap-20">

      <article class="border border-zinc-100/10 p-10 rounded-xl flex gap-y-5 flex-col items-center">
        <Clock width={48} class="text-red-500" aria-hidden="true" />
        <p class="text-red-500 text-medium">Time Wasted</p>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm">Countless hours lost on repetitive low-value tasks that AI could handle instantly.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border border-zinc-100/10 p-10 rounded-xl flex gap-y-5 flex-col items-center">
        <Money width={48} class="text-red-500" aria-hidden="true" />
        <p class="text-red-500 text-medium">Money Lost</p>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm">Missed leads and sales because your system can't keep up.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border border-zinc-100/10 p-10 rounded-xl flex gap-y-5 flex-col items-center">
        <Users width={48} class="text-red-500" aria-hidden="true" />
        <p class="text-red-500 text-medium">Staff Burnout</p>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm">Employees overwhelmed by routine work instead of focusing on growth-driving activities.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border border-zinc-100/10 p-10 rounded-xl flex gap-y-5 flex-col items-center">
        <ChatBubble width={48} class="text-red-500" aria-hidden="true" />
        <p class="text-red-500 text-medium">Slow Response = Lost Clients</p>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm">Delayed replies make prospects walk away to competitors who move faster.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-30" aria-labelledby="solution-heading">
    <h2 id="solution-heading" class="text-4xl text-zinc-100 text-center font-semibold">Our Solution</h2>
    <p class="text-secondary text-center">Running a business today means juggling endless tasks. Without automation, you're losing energy, time, money and customers every single day.</p>
  
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-10 xl:gap-20 mt-10">
      {
        mockData.solutions.map(solution => (
          <SolutionCard
            icon={solution.icon}
            title={solution.name}
            description={solution.description}
          />
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <!-- <div class="mt-10 px-4 py-10 bg-[#00B4FB]/10 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="text-center text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">Key Message</h3>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-zinc-200 text-center">We don't replace receptionists or assistants—we optimize repetitive processes so they can focus on customers and high-value tasks.</p>
    </div> -->
  </section>

  <section class="mt-30" id="pricecomp" aria-labelledby="benefits-heading">
    <h2 id="benefits-heading" class="text-4xl text-zinc-100 text-center font-semibold">Strategic Benefits of <span class="text-theme">AI</span></h2>

    <BenefitsComparison
      client:only
    />
  </section>

  <section class="mt-30" aria-labelledby="cases-heading">
    <h2 id="cases-heading" class="text-4xl text-zinc-100 text-center font-semibold">High Value Cases</h2>

    <div class="mt-20 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
      {
        mockData.highValueCases.map(hvc => (
          <SolutionCard
            icon={hvc.icon}
            title={hvc.name}
            description={hvc.description}
          />
        ))
      }
    </div>
 
  </section>

    <div class="py-20 flex flex-col items-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-zinc-950 mt-30 rounded-xl" aria-label="Risk-free setup offer">
      <div class="text-lg px-6 py-3 inline-flex rounded-xl items-center text-zinc-100 border border-zinc-100/10">
        <Shield width={32} class="mr-2" aria-hidden="true" />
        <span>Try Free 30 Days</span>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-4xl text-zinc-100 mt-10">Risk-Free Setup</h3>
      <p class="mt-5 sm:max-w-1/2 text-center text-secondary">Free setup for the first month: You try without risk. With demonstrable results, decide if you continue with a monthly subscription, or cancel without commitment.</p>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <CalWrapper>
          <a
            href="javascript:void(0)"
          >
            <Button>Start Free Trial</Button>
          </a>
        </CalWrapper>
      </div>
    </div>
</ServiceLayout>